{"tid":256781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【侵擾租客】外籍租客放單位上airbnb   黑警業主換鎖被捕","createTime":"2017-05-24T18:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T19:15:41.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"56b0eb003044d89b377ff2b308778ddbec025bcb","tid":256781,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T18:59:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">租客勝一仗！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170524/56737903\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170524%2F56737903&d=CssjnrJgIHn83GkITlzGY%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=52cd9ed4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170524%2F56737903&h=34cdfd81\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170524/56737903</a><br />\n<br />\n【23:05 更新】被捕女警去年將上址單位租給該名外籍男子，但其後發現他將單位透過airbnb再出租，兩人因此爭執<br />\n<br />\n中區警區重案組昨日拘捕及檢控一名30歲姓鍾女警一項「侵擾」罪，她涉嫌與32歲外籍男租客發生租務糾紛後，更換上環差館上街一單位的門鎖。案件將於下周一(29日)在東區裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，被捕女警去年將上址單位租給該名外籍男子，但其後發現他將單位透過airbnb再出租，兩人因此爭執。女警其後自行換單位門鎖。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。"},{"pid":"8640cae3e0e862068aad0c6aeb278dc400ab06fd","tid":256781,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T19:05:20.000Z","msg":"Yeung Wah James v. Alfa Sea Ltd.[1993]1HKC440 &ndash; 租客租用了一幢大廈三樓的一個單位，而整幢大廈由業主擁有。業主曾嘗試說服租客退租但不成功。某日，租客從外地回港，發覺門鎖被更換而不能進入其單位。此外，業主在未得到租客同意下，私自闖入單位並進行翻新工程。高等法院裁定業主嚴重違反寧靜享用物業的承諾，並判決業主向租客賠償$50,000一般性損失，以及$50,000懲罰性損失。"},{"pid":"f34bfe71198871c592eccf73528beb68d560886c","tid":256781,"uid":81099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T19:06:20.000Z","msg":"合約唔寫明不可分租？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b30dd5032c19aa17b01278b3ed074ada468114","tid":256781,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T19:07:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>合約唔寫明不可分租？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n合約寫都好, 業主都無得換鎖<br />\n<br />\n都係要跟程序去告, 去排期上庭搞收樓"},{"pid":"56d9dc18250a520b5937191688f8f5c975a61a45","tid":256781,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T19:07:43.000Z","msg":"有無寫明不可分租?"},{"pid":"07bfc26d55652b8d5429be3b69e7d03ef2781fa2","tid":256781,"uid":81099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T19:08:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>合約唔寫明不可分租？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n合約寫都好, 業主都無得換鎖<br />\n<br />\n都係要跟程序去告, 去排期上庭搞收樓</blockquote><br />\n廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n答非所問"},{"pid":"d3eccfb3259f64fb9ae5f0a20123e2b9d2b72258","tid":256781,"uid":81099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T19:09:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無寫明不可分租?</blockquote><br />\n樓主：合約寫都好, 業主都無得換鎖<br />\n<br />\n都係要跟程序去告, 去排期上庭搞收樓<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cba16880b91d8ff0b555b9ba486d5513d6e05dc4","tid":256781,"uid":73482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T19:10:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>合約唔寫明不可分租？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n合約寫都好, 業主都無得換鎖<br />\n<br />\n都係要跟程序去告, 去排期上庭搞收樓</blockquote><br />\n廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n答非所問</blockquote><br />\n正宗叻唔切，衝出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a27091b2c23927980d5ec2